Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuk! {\alpha&HFF&}Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuk! Wanna join us?
