Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'll pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen for the voice of God and never guess you will...
