Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,35 year old, Tofuji Naoki, is being held in custody charged with her murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Day after day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always the same news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely... {\alpha&HFF&}pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely... pointless...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is... {\alpha&HFF&}rotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is... rotting.
