Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another is the extinction of many species of life on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:44.13,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously went to see that shit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Species are becoming extinct at a faster rate than has occurred...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.13,0:03:45.56,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a complete waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.74,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,You get the feeling that they're just trying to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Literally translated as "a notebook of Death".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The human whose name is written in this note shall die"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sick though, it's no different to chain letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The human whose name is written in this note shall die"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be going insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This note will not take effect unless the writer has the person's face in their mind when they write his/her name."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Therefore, {\alpha&HFF&}people sharing the same name will not be affected."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Therefore, people sharing the same name will not be affected."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is written within 40 seconds of writing the person's name, it will happen as it is written".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If the cause of death is not specified, by default, the person will die of a heart attack".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.21,0:05:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Should a cause of death be specified, a further 6 minutes and 40 seconds are granted to write any further details".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this means you can either kill them quickly or painfully, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a lot of detail to go into for a simple prank... {\alpha&HFF&}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a lot of detail to go into for a simple prank... Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Writing a name causes someone to die...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the off-chance that someone actually does die, {\alpha&HFF&}wouldn't that make me a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the off-chance that someone actually does die, wouldn't that make me a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. {\alpha&HFF&}It'd never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. It'd never happen.
