Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The phantom killer who attacked six people in Shinjuku's business district yesterday, has now taken eight children and kindergarten teachers as hostages and is holed up in this nursery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police has identified the man as Otoharada Kurou, aged 42, unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they're about to begin negotiations...
