Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't help but feel extremely concerned for the safety of the hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to report from the scene at this present moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
