Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! {\alpha&HFF&}That stupid old hag isn't here to pick me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! That stupid old hag isn't here to pick me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.. {\alpha&HFF&}Thinking about this really makes you realize just how many people the world would actually be better off without.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.. Thinking about this really makes you realize just how many people the world would actually be better off without.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fancy having some fun with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Takuo-san for you, {\alpha&HFF&}you've certainly bagged another hottie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Takuo-san for you, you've certainly bagged another hottie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Shibuimaru Takuo, but you can call me Shibutaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang out with us for a while, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't trouble me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't want us to "trouble her"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, take them off for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.04,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,All the different variations of writing the name "Shibuimaru Takuo".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, {\alpha&HFF&}let's see what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see what happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuo! {\alpha&HFF&}Look out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.71,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuo! Look out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-{\alpha&HFF&}That settles it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That settles it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note.. {\alpha&HFF&}It's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Death Note.. It's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dickhead! {\alpha&HFF&}Why'd he jump out like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dickhead! Why'd he jump out like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... {\alpha&HFF&}I'd better get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... I'd better get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been five days since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... {\alpha&HFF&}I'd better get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... I'd better get going soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, {\alpha&HFF&}you going out somewhere, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, you going out somewhere, Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you go in our world, it'll only be desolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've dropped my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you really fucked up this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, didn't you cheat a second Death Note out of the Shinigami Overlord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you lost both of 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do ya even know where ya dropped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home. {\alpha&HFF&}You're pretty early today, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home. You're pretty early today, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm back, mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'm back, mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}Oh, you want the results of the national mock exams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, {\alpha&HFF&}you want the results of the national mock exams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, you want the results of the national mock exams, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! {\alpha&HFF&}Number one again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Number one again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really tried hard, didn't you, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. {\alpha&HFF&}I'm going to study in my room, so don't interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. I'm going to study in my room, so don't interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Light! {\alpha&HFF&}Do you want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Light! Do you want anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can ask for whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really, {\alpha&HFF&}mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already got what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see that you've taken quite a shine to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ryuk, {\alpha&HFF&}the Shinigami who dropped that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Ryuk, the Shinigami who dropped that notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.61,0:13:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by that face of yours earlier, {\alpha&HFF&}it seems you've already realized that that is no ordinary notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by that face of yours earlier, it seems you've already realized that that is no ordinary notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shinigami, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised, Ryuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, {\alpha&HFF&}I've been waiting for you, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I've been waiting for you, {\alpha&HFF&}Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I've been waiting for you, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already realized that this Shinigami's notebook is real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having already witnessed so many things, {\alpha&HFF&}has allowed me to act with conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having already witnessed so many things, has allowed me to act with conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {\alpha&HFF&}You surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, I've heard of instances where a Death Note has appeared in the human world, {\alpha&HFF&}but you're the first person to have written this many names in just five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past, I've heard of instances where a Death Note has appeared in the human world, but you're the first person to have written this many names in just five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, people are too frightened to write as much as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already prepared myself, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knowingly used a Shinigami's notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}and now a Shinigami has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knowingly used a Shinigami's notebook, and now a Shinigami has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to me? {\alpha&HFF&}Are you going to take my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to me? Are you going to take my soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? {\alpha&HFF&}What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.88,0:14:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of fantasy created by humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to do anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment that notebook fell to this world, {\alpha&HFF&}it became the property of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment that notebook fell to this world, it became the property of the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, {\alpha&HFF&}that notebook belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, that notebook belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-{\alpha&HFF&}Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want it, you can pass it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I reserve the right to erase your memory of the Death Note if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're telling me that there's really no trade-off for using the Death Note?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you insist on knowing, {\alpha&HFF&}there is the fear and suffering that is faced only by those humans who use Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you insist on knowing, there is the fear and suffering that is faced only by those humans who use Death Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, when you die, {\alpha&HFF&}it falls to me to write your name in my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, when you die, it falls to me to write your name in my Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume that a human who's used the Death Note can go to Heaven or Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have something to look forward to when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. {\alpha&HFF&}Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Answer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought you some apples. {\alpha&HFF&}The neighbours brought them round to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought you some apples. The neighbours brought them round to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so dark in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll ruin your eyesight you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? {\alpha&HFF&}Can't mother see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}don't read me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? Can't mother see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be my notebook, {\alpha&HFF&}so as the current user you're the only one who can see me, and of course the only one who can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be my notebook, so as the current user you're the only one who can see me, {\alpha&HFF&}and of course the only one who can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That used to be my notebook, so as the current user you're the only one who can see me, and of course the only one who can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Death Note is the bond that ties you, the human, to me, Ryuk, the Shinigami, so to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm, {\alpha&HFF&}nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one more thing.. {\alpha&HFF&}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one more thing.. Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, {\alpha&HFF&}apples in the human world are damn good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, apples in the human world are damn good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're.. how to say it.. {\alpha&HFF&}"juicy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're.. how to say it.. "juicy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't pick you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to drop the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, did you think you'd been picked because you're smart or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happened to fall around here, {\alpha&HFF&}and you just happened to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just happened to fall around here, and you just happened to pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wrote it in the most popular human language, English.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you drop it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went through the whole trouble of writing down instructions, {\alpha&HFF&}so don't tell me you just happened to drop it by accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went through the whole trouble of writing down instructions, so don't tell me you just happened to drop it by accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you say... {\alpha&HFF&}because I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.56,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you say... because I was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bored?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that most Shinigami haven't got much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They mainly sleep or gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.89,0:17:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try writing any names in your book, {\alpha&HFF&}and they'll laugh at you for trying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try writing any names in your book, and they'll laugh at you for trying too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you write the name of someone living in the Shinigami world, they won't die, {\alpha&HFF&}and it's no fun killing humans from the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you write the name of someone living in the Shinigami world, they won't die, and it's no fun killing humans from the Shinigami world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured it'd be more fun in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, {\alpha&HFF&}you seem to have written quite a few names here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you seem to have written quite a few names here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you only write the cause of death for the guy that was run over by a dump truck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't write the cause of death, {\alpha&HFF&}the victim dies of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't write the cause of death, the victim dies of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the best thing about the Death Note, Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already begun to exhaust the list of high profile criminals, {\alpha&HFF&}and I'm gradually starting to include those people that commit less serious crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already begun to exhaust the list of high profile criminals, and I'm gradually starting to include those people that commit less serious crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what does that achieve?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how stupid people are, {\alpha&HFF&}they'll eventually realize that someone is wiping out these criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how stupid people are, they'll eventually realize that someone is wiping out these criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to let the world know of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That there is someone who can, and will, pass righteous judgement!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you plan to achieve by passing this "righteous judgement"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... {\alpha&HFF&}I'm also bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... I'm also bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, at first I didn't believe it, {\alpha&HFF&}but that notebook has a kind of magic that compels humans to try it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, at first I didn't believe it, but that notebook has a kind of magic that compels humans to try it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I k-killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a life. The consequences can't be light.
